## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf75e-103">擴充辨別名稱的格式包含物件的 objectGUID 屬性的字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf75e-103">The extended form of a distinguished name includes a string representation of the objectGUID property of an object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf75e-104">例如使用者、 群組和電腦主體物件的安全性，擴充的表單也包含 [objectSID] 屬性的字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf75e-104">For security principal objects such as users, groups, and computers, the extended form also includes a string representation of the objectSID property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf75e-105">如需 objectGUID 和 objectSID 屬性的詳細資訊，請參閱主題[Object-guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp)並[物件 Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp)位於 MSDN Library， [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf75e-105">For more information about the objectGUID and objectSID properties, see the topics [Object-Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) and [Object-Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf75e-106">下列 C# 範例示範如何傳回十六進位格式的辨別名稱的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf75e-106">The following C# example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```
